LiVision includes third-party software components. Their licenses are provided in the source tree.

Included components (not exhaustive):
- bgfx, bx, bimg (see `third-party/bgfx.cmake/*/LICENSE`)
- Dear ImGui (see `third-party/livision/imgui/LICENSE.txt`)
- ImPlot (see `third-party/livision/implot/LICENSE`)
- bgfx-imgui (see `third-party/bgfx-imgui` and embedded license files)
- Other bgfx dependencies in `third-party/bgfx.cmake/bgfx/3rdparty` and `third-party/bgfx.cmake/bimg/3rdparty`

Please review the license files in the listed directories for full terms.
